Live.PluginDescription: Provides the live Visitor Log and lets you watch your visitors live in the real-time dashboard widget. The plugin also lets you see a Visitor profile for any given user.
Live.VisitorLogDocumentation: This table shows the latest sessions within the selected date range. You can see when a visitor's last session occurred by hovering over the date of a session. %1$s If the date range includes today, you can see your visitors real time! %2$s The data displayed here is always live, regardless of whether and how often you are using the archiving cron job.
